{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6029389404","title":"“学校不重视老教授和民主党派”","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8118740698","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"6029389404"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"386454d00a","name":"杨大美"},{"id":"4771ddecd4","name":"丁少飞"},{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"},{"id":"be5c925d21","name":"林墨荫"},{"id":"c108c896c5","name":"金荣新"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"db0463cf9e","type":"title","text":"“学校不重视老教授和民主党派”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6029389404"},{"id":"851eefff65","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院杨大美金荣新林墨荫丁少飞","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6029389404"},{"id":"cc74c1001b","type":"appellation","text":"杨大美说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6029389404"},{"id":"b75ef87caa","type":"appellation","text":"“学校不重视老教授和民主党派，尹副院长，王嘉荫等是党委逼走的，是由于党委不懂科学，骄傲自满，自以为是，把老教授看成思想落后”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6029389404"},{"id":"7ad94a6edf","type":"appellation","text":"金荣新说：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6029389404"},{"id":"8533385674","type":"appellation","text":"“老干部与知识分子之间的矛盾，只有在党的全部提高科学文化水平成为内行的时候才能解决。”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6029389404"},{"id":"48d8789116","type":"appellation","text":"“知识分子是宝贝，又是包袱，不打不行，打了又哭，很难办。”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6029389404"},{"id":"5fb36fa57e","type":"appellation","text":"“中国大知识分子不简单，不好领导，党没经验，在知识分子问题上摔了不少跤。”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6029389404"},{"id":"10bc793d58","type":"paragraph","text":"“工农出身的干部就是不能体会我自小资产阶级的城市出身的人，因此没法进行思想教育。”","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6029389404"},{"id":"1655f5ca2c","type":"appellation","text":"林墨荫说：","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6029389404"},{"id":"53789060c9","type":"appellation","text":"“我院主要矛盾是党委领导与知识分子的矛盾。”","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6029389404"},{"id":"6490034d71","type":"appellation","text":"丁少飞说：","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6029389404"},{"id":"3622acf634","type":"appellation","text":"“知识分子提意见最敏感，最尖锐，工人提不了什么意见。储安平的‘党天下’没有什么，你们（按：指党）就把人家从坏处想。”","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6029389404"}],"page":{"id":"2b396f4125","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6029389404","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}